00:45:12,660 --> 00:45:21,860
[Silver Rain Terrace]

559
00:45:35,190 --> 00:45:35,800
Fu,

560
00:45:36,670 --> 00:45:37,430
where's Zhuo Lanjiang?

561
00:45:37,800 --> 00:45:39,000
I haven't seen him for several days.

562
00:45:39,120 --> 00:45:39,760
Is he okay?

563
00:45:40,000 --> 00:45:41,320
Our Young Master went out of town
for some sect affairs.

564
00:45:41,520 --> 00:45:42,120
He is doing fine.

565
00:45:56,360 --> 00:45:58,670
What do you think
this piece of cloth is used for?

566
00:46:00,000 --> 00:46:01,710
What's the meaning of this pattern?

567
00:46:02,470 --> 00:46:03,760
Whether it is text or a pattern,

568
00:46:04,190 --> 00:46:05,000
