569
00:46:05,600 --> 00:46:06,560
A text?

570
00:46:10,000 --> 00:46:11,470
It'd be great if Jiang were here.

571
00:46:11,760 --> 00:46:13,760
The fabric shops in Heyang
all belong to Silver Rain Terrace.

572
00:46:14,080 --> 00:46:15,600
I received his message a few days ago.

573
00:46:15,670 --> 00:46:16,600
But there's been
no word from him since then.

574
00:46:16,710 --> 00:46:18,000
The spy in Silver Rain Terrace

575
00:46:18,280 --> 00:46:19,670
has something to do
with the Ripple Organization.

576
00:46:20,430 --> 00:46:22,080
Maybe he's facing some difficulties now.

577
00:46:22,950 --> 00:46:24,470
I'll ask someone
at Silver Rain Terrace later.

578
00:46:25,470 --> 00:46:26,390
I'll go with you.

579
00:46:28,040 --> 00:46:29,040
It's mealtime.

580
00:46:37,150 --> 00:46:38,000
Young Lady, Mr. Pan,

581
00:46:38,390 --> 00:46:39,190
have a taste.

582
00:46:39,360 --> 00:46:40,710
It's a new dish
I've been experimenting with.

583
00:46:40,840 --> 00:46:41,670
Let me know if it tastes good.

584
00:46:41,800 --> 00:46:42,520
Definitely delicious.

585
00:46:43,470 --> 00:46:44,630
You haven't tasted it yet.

586
00:46:44,760 --> 00:46:45,560
How do you know it's delicious?

587
00:46:45,630 --> 00:46:46,390
Of course I know.

588
00:46:46,560 --> 00:46:47,670
Your cooking never tastes bad.

589
00:46:56,800 --> 00:46:58,950
Young Lady, try this first.

590
00:46:59,040 --> 00:47:00,000
- You'll definitely like this.
- All right.

591
00:47:04,800 --> 00:47:06,910
What's this white thing?

592
00:47:09,230 --> 00:47:10,840
I cut my hand while chopping vegetables.

593
00:47:10,910 --> 00:47:12,430
It must be the saltwater

594
00:47:12,470 --> 00:47:13,760
Ze used to clean the wound.

595
00:47:14,430 --> 00:47:15,230
Salt?

596
00:47:22,670 --> 00:47:23,230
Ling.

597
00:47:23,560 --> 00:47:24,870
Did you wash the clothes
I wore the other day?

598
00:47:25,320 --> 00:47:25,910
Not yet.

599
00:47:26,320 --> 00:47:27,190
Take them to me.

600
00:47:30,760 --> 00:47:32,800
When I came out of the cave
at the back mountain the other day,

601
00:47:32,870 --> 00:47:34,000
my skirt hem looked like this.

602
00:47:34,360 --> 00:47:35,360
The situation was urgent back then,

603
00:47:35,430 --> 00:47:36,520
so I didn't think much about it.

604
00:47:37,320 --> 00:47:38,390
Now that I think about it,

605
00:47:39,670 --> 00:47:42,230
