got into the river and got wet.

607
00:47:44,520 --> 00:47:45,470
So it means

608
00:47:45,870 --> 00:47:46,840
that the things they stored in the cave

609
00:47:46,950 --> 00:47:48,230
were bags of salt.

610
00:47:48,670 --> 00:47:49,710
Because it was salt,

611
00:47:49,800 --> 00:47:51,120
there was inevitably some spillage

612
00:47:51,190 --> 00:47:52,120
during transportation.

613
00:47:52,230 --> 00:47:53,230
Salt got into the river,

614
00:47:53,600 --> 00:47:55,190
and the salt concentration
in the water was too high,

615
00:47:55,520 --> 00:47:56,670
causing all the fish
in the river to die.

616
00:47:58,000 --> 00:48:00,150
There's surprisingly
a lot of illegal salt.

617
00:48:01,520 --> 00:48:03,760
No wonder it took Mr. Chen years
to put effort

618
00:48:03,840 --> 00:48:05,390
