627
00:48:52,800 --> 00:48:53,360
Ze.

628
00:48:53,470 --> 00:48:54,000
Yes.

629
00:48:54,280 --> 00:48:55,040
Post a notice.

630
00:48:55,120 --> 00:48:56,230
Mr. Chen is wanted throughout the city.

631
00:48:56,560 --> 00:48:57,080
Yes.

632
00:48:58,780 --> 00:49:05,380
