00:49:10,320 --> 00:49:11,520
Xiaosheng, why are you here?

637
00:49:14,470 --> 00:49:16,390
I have a business to discuss
with you alone.

638
00:49:16,390 --> 00:49:17,390
Please... Please come over here.

639
00:49:17,870 --> 00:49:20,040
Xiaosheng, just say it.

640
00:49:20,360 --> 00:49:22,080
There are no secrets
between Mr. Pan and me anymore.

